title: unDraw
description: Browse to find the images that fit your needs and click to download. Use the on-the-fly color image generation to match your brand identity.

title: Happy Hues
description: See color palette inspiration on a real example website. As you click on different palettes every color on this site updates to give you context of how that color could be used for your design or illustration projects.

title: Unsplash
description: Beautiful free images and photos that you can download and use in any project. Better than any stock or royalty-free photo.

title: svghub
description: SVG Hub | Custom-color elements ready to paste into your project.

title: JSON Data AI
description: Get JSON data about anything depending on your prompt.

title: Tabler Icons
description: 4694 free and open source SVG icons designed with attention to detail to make your design stand out. Highly customizable. No attribution required. For commercial use.

title: Squoosh
description: Squoosh is the ultimate image optimizer that allows you to compress and compare images with different codecs in your browser.

title: Color Designer
description: The main purpose of this tool is to help with building a color palette and generate tints and shades based on it. Just pick a color, and the app does the rest. You can use the preselected colors or the color picker for more control.

title: Type Scale
description: Preview and choose the right type scale for your project. Experiment with font size, scale and different webfonts.
